{"tid":1435684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Ann姐又有嘢想同香港人講！！","createTime":"2019-08-09T06:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:43:35.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f8aa26f6766322a73093bbd1743fefb77ba64e2f","tid":1435684,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:15:05.000Z","msg":"香港人真的受夠了，是時候叫停了！我們理解部分香港人希望和平表達訴求，也感謝警務人員過去一段時間的辛勞與汗水，為了我們共同的家，我們呼籲全體香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n1.亂夠了：停止無休的遊行、集會、佔路<br />\n2.停暴力：停止一切掟汽油彈、掟磚、打鬥的衝擊行為<br />\n3.勿擾民：停止影響市民日常生活的「不合作運動」<br />\n4.止破壞：停止破壞警署和公共交通設施<br />\n5.守法治：回復守法傳統，勿自毀「一國兩制」<br />\n6.阻撕裂：不同政治取向市民，不再互相攻擊                               <br />\n7.返正軌：社會回到正軌，政府改革向前<br />\n <br />\n香港已經遍體<span style=\"color: red;\">鳞</span>傷，不能再忍氣吞聲、姑息縱容。政府要痛定思痛，儘快止住亂局，在社會民生上改革向前，令市民生活得更好。<br />\n<br />\n700萬香港人應攜手同心，為我們自己，也為下一代，向暴力和亂象勇敢說不！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/537711586254667/posts/3555497291142733/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F537711586254667%2Fposts%2F3555497291142733%2F&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzaZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=604db749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/537711586254667/posts/3555497291142733/</a>"},{"pid":"62c3f81b31e36253334e42e12bff61e9e32a822e","tid":1435684,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3a3VhGw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3a3VhGw.jpg&h=7c86973c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df5b141678bbb1381e6fab1228bfcd03a717947d","tid":1435684,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:18:19.000Z","msg":"Ann姐可能太激動 打咗個殘體字出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要體諒下佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c321fac6ca8bf9d40afc75b880d1e21c5742ee8","tid":1435684,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi